| Being authenticated  |                      |                       |
| proves identity. It  | HTTPS protects the   | Security through      |
| says nothing about   | token in transit. It | obscurity is not      |
| what resources or    | does not protect a   | authorisation. Any    |
| actions are          | token with no        | URL or API endpoint   |
