  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **The test:** for any endpoint in your application, can you answer all
  three questions independently? **(1) How does the server know who this
  is? (2) How does the server verify they are who they claim? (3) How
  does the server decide whether this identity is permitted to perform
  this action on this specific resource? If any answer is \"it trusts the
  client\" --- that is the vulnerability.**

